{"tid":2281981,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"王婆婆旺角舉黃傘　警指影響公共秩序","createTime":"2020-11-11T13:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T04:08:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":573,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"bac85abc7c20994fba5f8ebbd339d3a8b121db56","tid":2281981,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/124261487_3635449033207357_7777416288226745437_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=v8gUa8Y8ucIAX-fSX_x&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=60df007da459062e12019340f9c19fdb&amp;oe=5FD20E75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F124261487_3635449033207357_7777416288226745437_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3Dv8gUa8Y8ucIAX-fSX_x%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3D60df007da459062e12019340f9c19fdb%26oe%3D5FD20E75&h=957aef98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚上約 8 時 45 分，拿著英國國旗款式手袋的王婆婆，在沙田響應出席同一活動後，再專程來到旺角，在朗豪坊外高舉黃色傘，展示寫有「Fight for freedom，Stand with HK」燈箱，並不時舉起「Save 12 HK YOUTHS」紙牌。<br />\n<br />\n約 15 分鐘後，原本在對面行人路舉機拍攝的警員，走到朗豪坊門外以橙帶圍起王婆婆，指她影響公共秩序，並要求她收起展示的物品，又稱現場已有 50 人聚集；王婆婆拒絕離開，稱只得她一人，並持續跟警員理論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3635449149874012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F3635449149874012&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=6cca189a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3635449149874012</a>"},{"pid":"6377260bb6b187cde8adf860d048fc337f1c48e8","tid":2281981,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:34:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ec3b94234d457ea6733be02f5fc3b77ca364684","tid":2281981,"uid":2419,"like":72,"dislike":3,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:34:56.000Z","msg":"d燈箱幾靚喎"},{"pid":"730f354fdf9feb02c841cdb17