/i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F124261487_3635449033207357_7777416288226745437_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3Dv8gUa8Y8ucIAX-fSX_x%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3D60df007da459062e12019340f9c19fdb%26oe%3D5FD20E75&h=957aef98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚上約 8 時 45 分，拿著英國國旗款式手袋的王婆婆，在沙田響應出席同一活動後，再專程來到旺角，在朗豪坊外高舉黃色傘，展示寫有「Fight for freedom，Stand with HK」燈箱，並不時舉起「Save 12 HK YOUTHS」紙牌。<br />\n<br />\n約 15 分鐘後，原本在對面行人路舉機拍攝的警員，走到朗豪坊門外以橙帶圍起王婆婆，指她影響公共秩序，並要求她收起展示的物品，又稱現場已有 50 人聚集；王婆婆拒絕離開，稱只得她一人，並持續跟警員理論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3635449149874012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F3635449149874012&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=6cca189a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3635449149874012</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"非常尊敬黃婆婆"},{"pid":"5a20e1b67926e75f6d6d6885184808f7ed3dc719","tid":2281981,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:36:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2cc61bd66b882bfdcca949b671e0c4f8ddda3ca","tid":2281981,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffef1081ee09154e73dff0887d5046bcd6d347bd","tid":2281981,"uid":148447,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"一把年紀就留返係屋企養老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80101438469b9b6f14d0f25ae966abdb1e06f329","tid":2281981,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbc13d3a09f5127169e47ad8e9efc71fca0669e4","tid":2281981,"uid":4838,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d96fea84b4ff86d03f776ec482fe70ee1f90f4","tid":2281981,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4ee92711ce0e9a0be055e992d507027303d